    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 in concours-level condition. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system for optimized torque across the rev range. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including a reinforced rear subframe and rod bearing replacement. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics with aluminum components for reduced unsprung weight. The exterior finish is flawless, exhibiting no paint depth irregularities or swirl marks, while the interior leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A mechanically perfect specimen for the purist collector.",
